---
// Component: FAQ.astro
// Purpose: Frequently asked questions section to address user concerns
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        Everything you need to know about recipe nutrition analysis
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <details class="group bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-open:text-lemon-600 dark:group-open:text-lemon-400 transition-colors">
            How accurate are the nutrition calculations?
          </h3>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Our AI achieves 90-95% accuracy by using comprehensive nutrition databases (USDA, global food data) 
            and intelligent portion estimation. For ingredients with unclear quantities ("a pinch of salt"), 
            we use conservative estimates. Professional nutritionists use our tool as a starting point for their calculations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <details class="group bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-open:text-lemon-600 dark:group-open:text-lemon-400 transition-colors">
            What recipe formats does it support?
          </h3>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We handle all common recipe formats: traditional ingredient lists, paragraph-style recipes, 
            mixed units (cups, grams, tablespoons), and even handwritten family recipes. 
            The AI understands natural language like "a handful of spinach" or "medium-sized onion" 
            and converts them to standard measurements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <details class="group bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-open:text-lemon-600 dark:group-open:text-lemon-400 transition-colors">
            Can it handle dietary restrictions and substitutions?
          </h3>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Yes! Our premium features include dietary adaptation suggestions (keto, vegan, gluten-free) 
            and ingredient substitutions with recalculated nutrition. For example, swap regular flour 
            for almond flour and get updated carb counts instantly. We support 15+ dietary patterns.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <details class="group bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-open:text-lemon-600 dark:group-open:text-lemon-400 transition-colors">
            How much does it cost?
          </h3>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We offer a generous free tier with 10 recipe analyses per month. 
            Our Pro plan ($9/month) includes unlimited analyses, dietary adaptations, 
            meal planning tools, and nutrition goal tracking. Perfect for serious home cooks and nutrition professionals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <details class="group bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-open:text-lemon-600 dark:group-open:text-lemon-400 transition-colors">
            Do you store my recipes?
          </h3>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Your privacy matters. We only store nutrition results (not full recipes) to improve our accuracy. 
            If you create an account, you can save your favorite analyses for easy access. 
            All data is encrypted and you can delete your account anytime. We never share personal recipe data.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <details class="group bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-open:text-lemon-600 dark:group-open:text-lemon-400 transition-colors">
            Can I use this for meal planning?
          </h3>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Absolutely! Many users analyze their weekly recipes to plan balanced meals that hit their macro targets. 
            Our Pro plan includes meal planning templates, weekly nutrition summaries, 
            and integration with popular meal planning apps. Perfect for batch cooking and prep.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <details class="group bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer select-none">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-open:text-lemon-600 dark:group-open:text-lemon-400 transition-colors">
            When will the full app be available?
          </h3>
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We're launching in early 2024! Early access members get first dibs on the beta, 
            special pricing, and the ability to influence which features we build first. 
            Join our waitlist to be notified the moment we go live.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Still have questions CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="bg-lemon-50 dark:bg-lemon-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Still have questions?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Our team is here to help! Reach out and we'll get back to you within 24 hours.
        </p>
        <button class="bg-lemon-500 hover:bg-lemon-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200">
          Contact Support
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 